latestPosts.caption:
Look 2 : Pre Muhurtham🤍💛

So many emotions were running through my mind just moments before the muhurtham. With only a few minutes left for the wedding, we managed to capture these beautiful pictures in a paruthi vayal near the mandapam😂. This saree’s color truly elevated the entire look! I got it from @prakash_silks_and_sarees , and the blouse, adorned with minimal pearl detailing, was beautifully designed by @ashtag_sewing .

I always wanted a thamarai jadai, and choosing it was the best decision—the pink hue of the real flowers added an extra touch of bliss. Amidst all the chaos, @navz_makeoverartistry beautifully brought the whole look together!

This soft, elegant reception look came alive through the hands of a dream team. Every detail rich, every element full of style and grace.

Makeup by me @dees_magictouch_ : Crafted a soft glam look to match the richness of the designer saree. subtle, radiant, and graceful.

Hairstyling @sai_uma_hairstylist : A flawless finish by a truly skilled hairstylist who knew exactly what the look needed

Costume design @niga_designers : Unique and beautifully detailed, the designer nailed every inch of this saree

Jewellery @aishi_jewellery : Handpicked pieces that elevated the entire look with their elegance and charm

Model @ranjaneeee : The cutest muse. graceful, patient, and a total natural in front of the camera!

Photography @vino_francis_roy : Captured to perfection, every angle and emotion framed with clarity and creativity.

Every element worked in harmony, and the result speaks for itself.
